":"能参加这么重要的活动，PAREO非常紧张，\n但难得有这个机会，PAREO也要……送上一句话……！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"ev216-ep3-068","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"无论是麻弥同学打鼓时那认真的表情，\n还是那略带羞涩的笑容，又或是开心地聊着器材时，\n那天真无邪的眼眸，PAREO全部全部全部都喜欢~~~！！！！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"ev216-ep3-069","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"麻弥同学！今后PAREO还会为您那\n一往直前的身姿，还有可爱的举止，\n全心全意地送上声援！！！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"ev216-ep3-070","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"伊芙","body":"麻弥同学，恭喜你毕业","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"ev216-ep3-071","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"